r%20jobs%20is%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20familiar%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20is%20Allison%20Kirkby%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20British%20telecommunications%20giant%20BT.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fc8d41424-f2d9-418e-8da2-55823f1c22ca%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20Sunday%2C%20Kirkby%20said%20that%20advancements%20in%20AI%20technology%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20cuts%20at%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBT%20announced%20in%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-telecom-ceo-ai-replace-jobs-chatgpt-bt-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20cut%20up%20to%2055%2C000%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202030%20as%20part%20of%20a%20push%20to%20reduce%20its%20cost%20base%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kirkby%20told%20the%20FT%20that%20this%20plan%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20reflect%26quot%3B%20AI's%20%26quot%3Bfull%20potential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20what%20we%20learn%20from%20AI%E2%80%89...%20there%20may%20be%20an%20opportunity%20for%20BT%20to%20be%20even%20smaller%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBT%20has%20turned%20to%20AI%20in%20recent%20years%20to%20reinvent%20processes%20in%20areas%20like%20customer%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20announced%20in%202024%20that%20it%20was%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20aid%20sales%20and%20support%20operations%20across%20BT%20and%20EE%2C%20its%20mobile%20network%20division.%20In%20December%2C%20the%20firm%20said%20that%20EE's%20virtual%20assistant%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BAimee%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20handling%20up%20to%2060%2C000%20customer%20conversations%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBT%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20its%20attempts%20to%20automate%20such%20tasks.%20Swedish%20payments%20company%20Klarna%20has%20been%20open%20about%20its%20efforts%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20run%20its%20customer%20service%20desks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Klarna%20said%20its%20OpenAI-powered%20AI%20assistant%20was%20carrying%20out%20the%20work%20of%20700%20full-time%20customer%20service%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20CEO%2C%20Sebastian%20Siemiatkowski%2C%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20advocate%20of%20AI%20but%20has%20since%20softened%20his%20position%20on%20the%20tech%2C%20saying%20in%20May%20that%20certain%20cost-cutting%20efforts%20had%20gone%20too%20far%20and%20that%20Klarna%20was%20now%20recruiting%20for%20its%20customer%20service%20operation%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Siemiatkowski%20has%20remained%20confident%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-ai-may-cause-recession-white-collar-jobs-threat-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20poses%20a%20major%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20white-collar%20jobs%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20The%20Times%20Tech%20podcast%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20said%20that%20the%20technology%20had%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20gains%26quot%3B%20at%20Klarna%20and%20that%20its%20workforce%20had%20reduced%20from%20about%205%2C500%20to%203%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20suspicion%20again%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20an%20implication%20for%20white-collar%20jobs%2C%20and%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20that%20usually%20leads%20to%20at%20least%20a%20recession%20in%20the%20short%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20how%20we%20could%20avoid%20that%2C%20with%20what's%20happening%20from%20a%20technology%20perspective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20companies%20themselves%20have%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20that%20their%20product%20could%20significantly%20impact%20the%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-c