ious!%20Cute!%20Fun!%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20were%20all%20of%20the%20above.%20They%20were%20delightful%20and%20playful%2C%20but%20also%20super%20delicious.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20dish%20that%20just%20looks%20good%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20lunch%20was%20a%20good%20reminder%20that%20sometimes%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-teamlab-planets-museum-review-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etourist%20trap%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20can%20still%20be%20worth%20trying.%20It's%20a%20lesson%20we%20embraced%20as%20we%20walked%20through%20Takeshita%20Street%20and%20tried%20glazed%20strawberries%20on%20skewers%20and%20tornado%20potatoes%20%E2%80%94%20both%20delicious!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you're%20heading%20to%20Japan%2C%20seek%20out%20the%20hidden%20gems%2C%20but%20don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20try%20a%20few%20of%20the%20TikTok%20spots.%20Sometimes%20waiting%20in%20line%20is%20worth%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-souffle-pancakes-review-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749990841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684342faf748d8c055f33bb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-souffle-pancakes-review-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20jiggly%20souffl%C3%A9%20pancakes%20are%20a%20famous%20dish%20in%20Japan.%20We%20tried%20them%20at%20Micasadeco%20%26amp%3B%20Cafe%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20and%20they%20were%20worth%20waiting%20an%20hour%20in%20line%20for.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akonstantinides%40businessinsider.com%20(Anneta%20Konstantinides)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-souffle-pancakes-review-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7