g%20on%20California%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20where%20robotaxis%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20majority%20of%20respondents%20%E2%80%94%20about%2070%25%20%E2%80%94%20said%20they%20prefer%20%26quot%3Bthe%20experience%20of%20Waymo%20vs%20a%20regular%20rideshare%20with%20a%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20costs%20become%20a%20factor%2C%2042.7%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%2C%20but%20it%20would%20depend%20on%20how%20much%20more%20it%20would%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%2016.3%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20pay%20up%20to%20%2410%20more%2C%20while%2010.1%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20pay%20up%20to%20%245.%20Another%2016.3%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20would%20only%20pay%20less%20than%20%245.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%2039.1%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20would%20only%20pay%20the%20same%20or%20less%20for%20a%20Waymo%20and%2026.8%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20wouldn't%20take%20one%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20study%20doesn't%20factor%20in%20tipping%20to%20the%20final%20cost%20of%20an%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%2C%2026%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20that%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-self-driving-robotaxi-cars-without-drivers-amazing-tech-review-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprefer%20Waymo%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20leave%20a%20tip%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Waymo%20fans%20who%20have%20previously%20spoken%20to%20Business%20Insider%20point%20to%20this%20flexibility%20and%20the%20overall%20experience%20of%20having%20a%20car%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20is%20simply%20a%20better%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKevin%20Hartz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20VC%20and%20early%20Uber%20angel%20investor%2C%20told%20BI%20back%20in