0Cassie%20Ventura%20testifying%20at%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20sex-trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20trial.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683f48559b2a601d01b23a1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECassie%20Ventura%20testified%20during%20the%20first%20week%20of%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20sex-trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20trial.%3Cp%3EJane%20Rosenberg%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20texts%20show%20their%20apparent%20humiliation%20and%20regret%20over%20these%20marathons.%20On%20the%20witness%20stand%2C%20both%20women%20testified%20that%20they%20only%20pretended%20to%20enjoy%20themselves%20at%20the%20time%20due%20to%20Combs'%20violence%20and%20their%20emotional%20and%20financial%20dependence%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20women%20say%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebroke%20up%20with%20Combs%20repeatedly%20during%20these%20relationships%20%E2%80%94%20often%20after%20seeing%20him%20in%20social%20media%20posts%20dating%20other%20women%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20return%20after%20he%20promised%20to%20treat%20them%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20after%20the%20abuse%2C%20they're%20still%20coming%20back%20to%20Diddy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Chutkow%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Dykema%20and%20a%20former%20federal%20prosecutor%20in%20Michigan%20who%20has%20prosecuted%20cases%20involving%20organized%20crime%20and%20sex%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20plant%20the%20seed%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20jurors%2C%20well%2C%20if%20he%20really%20is%20this%20monster%2C%20and%20they're%20out%20there%20back%20in%20the%20real%20world%20amongst%20everyone%20else%2C%20why%20would%20they%20be%20drawn%20back%3F%26quot%3B%20Chutkow%20said%20of%20the%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20diametrically%20opposite%20worldview%20to%20that%20presented%20by%20federal%20pr