0of%20land%20and%20comparatively%20much%20reduced%20effort%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bringing%20back%20lost%20green%20cover.%20Native%20species%20of%20plants%20are%20grown%20together%20in%20a%20small%20space.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20a%20few%20more%20hands%20from%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20this%20can%20be%20an%20effective%20solution%20for%20a%20faster%20and%20greener%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Solar-powered%20cooling%20stations%20for%20slum%20residents%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%3A%20Jodhpur%2C%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%3A%20Local%20communities%2C%20supported%20by%20Natural%20Resources%20Defense%20Council%20(NRDC)%20and%20partners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20they%20did%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJodhpur%2C%20infamous%20for%20its%20extreme%20summer%20heat%2C%20often%20records%20temperatures%20above%2045%20degrees%20Celsius.%20For%20residents%20in%20low-income%20settlements%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20uncomfortable%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20dangerous.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20Heat%20Action%20Plan%2C%20solar-powered%20cooling%20stations%20were%20set%20up%20in%20densely%20populated%20areas%20to%20offer%20people%20a%20much-needed%20break%20from%20the%20relentless%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20portable%20cooling%20stations%20come%20with%20solar%20panels%2C%20mist%20fans%2C%20and%20natural%20features%20like%20grass%20roofs%20to%20cool%20the%20area.%20The%20design%20is%20simple%20but%20smart.%20They%20can%20be%20relocated%20depending%20on%20the%20heat%20risk%2C%20like%20shifting%20them%20near%20bus%20stops%2C%20markets%2C%20or%20crowded%20colonies.%20Women%20and%20youth%20volunteers%20manage%20these%20stations%2C%20helping%20locals%20stay%20hydrated%20and%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20drove%20this%20change%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20hubs%20bring%20the%20temperature%20down%20in%20real-time%20and%20creat