i%20campus%20is%20an%20oasis%20of%20colour%20and%20learning%20in%20Aurangabad%2C%20where%20youth%20can%20learn%20vocational%20skills%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMetal%20as%20a%20building%20alternative%20was%20nascent%20in%20India%2C%20and%20Akash%20was%20keen%20to%20push%20the%20envelope.%20Within%20four%20months%2C%20the%20project%20transitioned%20from%20a%20concept%20note%20to%20being%20fully%20operational.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20the%20year%2C%20Aurangabad%20is%20dry%20and%20hot.%20Nature%20has%20coloured%20the%20landscape%20in%20shades%20of%20brown.%20But%20the%20Pratham%20vocational%20training%20centre%20subverts%20the%20setting%20with%20its%20kaleidoscopic%20exteriors%20that%20mimic%20the%20creativity%20burgeoning%20within%2C%20where%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366571%2Fkalpana-sankar-hand-in-hand-india-access-to-financial-inclusion-tamil-nadu-percy-barnevik%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20workshops%20and%20skill%20training%20are%20held%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20centre%20is%20architecturally%20succinct%20%E2%80%94%20it%20sits%20on%20a%201%2C500-square-foot%20area%20of%20land%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20shipping%20containers%20lend%20it%20a%20kind%20of%20nomadism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajesh%20Narayan%20Thokale%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20vocational%20arm%20at%20Pratham%2C%20also%20a%20civil%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20with%20shipping%20containers%2C%20considering%20we%20could%20establish%20a%20structure%20like%20this%20in%20the%20catchment%20villages%20and%20run%20programmes%20for%20all%20age%