%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447991%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20standard%20PG%20room%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Picture%20source%3A%2099acres%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20PGs%2C%20many%20fear%20that%20Bengaluru%20could%20become%20even%20harder%20to%20enter%20for%20first-generation%20professionals%2C%20those%20from%20smaller%20towns%2C%20or%20anyone%20without%20strong%20financial%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESigns%20of%20change%3A%20Could%20Bengaluru%20rebalance%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20BBMP%20may%20review%20its%20stricter%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20June%202024%2C%20BBMP%20officials%20confirmed%20they%20are%20re-examining%20some%20of%20the%20rigid%20guidelines%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%2040-foot%20road-width%20rule%20that%20disqualified%20hundreds%20of%20PGs.%20While%20safety%20remains%20a%20priority%2C%20officials%20have%20acknowledged%20that%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20rule%20may%20not%20work%20for%20every%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2%EF%B8%8F)%20PG%20owners%20are%20engaging%20with%20civic%20bodies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EInstead%20of%20confrontation%2C%20PG%20associations%20are%20opening%20structured%20dialogues%20with%20BBMP%20and%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB).%20Many%20are%20requesting%20that%20PGs%20be%20classified%20as%20residential%20units%2C%20which%20could%20significantly%20ease%20costs%20related%20to%20water%2C%20sewerage%2C%20and%20trade%20licences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%EF%B8%8F)%20A%20possible%20blueprint%20for%20balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3EThese%20discussions%20signal%20that%20Bengaluru%20may%20be%20inching%20towards%20a%20more%20balanced%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20allows%20for%20both%20safe%2C%20regulated%20PG%20operations%20and%20continued%20affordability%20for%20newcomers%20who%20rely%20on%20these%20trans